    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering with its S54B32 power plant. This unit features a flawlessly synced double-VANOS system and pristine individual throttle bodies, delivering linear power through the entire 8,000 RPM sweep. The chassis integrity is absolute, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and recent rod bearing prophylaxis to ensure long-term mechanical reliability. Power is delivered via a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M-differential lock, providing exceptional rotational feedback. The suspension geometry remains true to factory specifications with no bushing deflection or damper fatigue. Finished in a concours-level exterior with zero paint metered deviations and an interior devoid of bolster wear or pixel degradation, this vehicle represents a turnkey opportunity for the serious collector.",
